CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 30, 1958, pg. A1, reads: "Oops! - Pretty Sarah Burney, 767 Anaheim St., almost slips from her lofty perch atop the diving board of a local swimming pool, but balances neatly for the photographer. The pretty and shapely lass lists dancing and swimming as her hobbies and plans to enter school next February. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Sarah Burney wearing light colored one piece strapless bathing suit with dark pattern along bust line, leaning against swimming pool ladder, at Ammon Recreation Center
